{"tid":1202533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中] 大家由而家開始用番密碼解鎖, 唔好用指模/Face ID","createTime":"2019-06-11T09:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:39:41.000Z","uid":231040,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"37b3d55e1d414a537ba3939783f6d3d49d848809","tid":1202533,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"黑警今日開始全港性行動, PTU/便衣齊出, 見人就搜袋盤問<br />\n<br />\n大家電話冇Set密碼嘅, 由而家開始記得用密碼(越多字數越好); 用緊指模/FaceID解鎖嘅就關咗佢用番密碼<br />\n<br />\n仲有係, 如無必要, 唔好帶一啲可以俾警犬入到你嘅物品喺身; 如果需要帶嘅, 請有多幾個同伴一齊, 同埋用大型交通工具做Yim護; 盡量用最多人用嘅入口去會場(e.g. 海富)以減低俾狗咬嘅機會~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/NACaPU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/NACaPU</a>"},{"pid":"4975b39abc3d3cb7abff01e4e39a1ae36c5f8c3b","tid":1202533,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:41:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d50b7ac367143b4b263b1c6f6439fd9e6bbbdbb","tid":1202533,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7dec1268ed83a2fa956b9dd790432b918c0985","tid":1202533,"uid":42536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"有用資訊要推"},{"pid":"3bdf2e0d7be8a49b15a0617effe219fbe150b987","tid":1202533,"uid":231040,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"如果帶咗嘢又俾警犬周到嘅話, 切記 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以唔駛講任何嘢</span> (因為呢個係你嘅公民權利嚟, 唔好俾狗凶到)"},{"pid":"4f649e591cd8cc25196264003000458208ba1b01","tid":1202533,"uid":231040,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有係 - 你係無義務要打開手機嘅內容俾狗睇, 佢係無權咁做, 要有法庭搜令至得</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">小心行事, 唔好咁易俾狗凶到</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"45b1bfa5bea6b30a69bacd59af593c9d60912c07","tid":12025